ll, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002258, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "But You my God, are Ever Living, Subsistent, slumber or sleep does not overtake you and one thing does not occupy You from another; the doors of Your sky are open for he who asks You and Your treasures are never locked and the doors of Your mercy are never covered and Your benefits are never forbidden for he who asks You rather they are given generously.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "WA ANTA ILAA-HEE HAIY-YOON QAIYYOO-MOON LAA TAA KHOZO-KA SENA-TOON WA LAA NAW-MOON WA LAA YASH-GHALO-KA SHAI-OON A’N SHAI-IN AB-WAABO SAMAA-E-KA LEMAN DA-AA’KA MO-FATTA-HAA-TOON WA KHAZAA-E-NOKA GHAIRO MO-GHALLA-QAA-TIN WA AB-WAABO RAHMATE-KA GHAIRO MAHJOO-BAA-TIN WA FAWAA-E-DOKA LEMAN SA-ALAKA GHAIRO MAHZOO-RAA-TIN BAL HEYA MABZOO-LAA-TOON.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَنْتَ اِلٰهِیْ حَیٌّ قَیٌّوْمٌ لَا تَاخُذُكَ سِنَۃٌ وَّلَا نَوْمٌ وَلَا یَشْغَلُكَ شَیْءٌ عَنْ شَیْءٍ اَبْوَابُ سَمَائِكَ لِمَنْ دَعَاكَ مُفَتَّحَاتٌ وَخَزَائِنُكَ غَیْرُ مُغَلَّقَاتٍ وَاَبْوَابُ رَحْمَتِكَ غَیْرُ مَحْجُوْبَاتٍ وَفَوَائِدُكَ لِمَنْ سَاَلَكَ غَیْرُ مَحْظُوْرَاتٍ بَلْ هِیَ مَبْذُوْلَاتٌ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1010489, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "You are my God, the Generous who does not turn away a beseecher who asks from You and You do not conceal Yourself from anyone of the believers who intends You no, by Your honor and Your Majesty no one removes their needs other than You and no one fulfills their needs apart from You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": "ANTA ILAAHEE AL-KAREE-MUL LAZEE LAA TARUDDO SAA-E-LAN MENAL MO-MENEENA SA-ALAKA WA LAA TAHTE-JEBO A’N AHA-DIN MIN-HUM ARAA-DAKA LAA WA I’ZZATE-KA WA JALAALE-KA WA LAA TUKH-TAZA-LO HAWAA-E-JA-HUM DOO-NAKA WA LAA YAQZEE-HAA AHA-DUN GHAIRO-KA.", "ArabicText1": "اَنْتَ اِلٰهِیْ اَلْكَرِیْمُ الَّذِیْ لَا تَرُدُّسَائِلًا مِنَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ سَاَلَكَ وَلَا تَحْتَجِبُ عَنْ اَحَدٍ مِّنْهُمْ اَرَادَكَ لَا وَعِزَّتِكَ وَجَلَالِكَ وَلَا تُخْتَزَلُ حَوَائِجَهُمْ دُوْنَكَ وَلَا یَقْضِیْهَا اَحَدٌ غَیْرُكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "Arab